  "intent": "Execute PCR sample pooling protocol using four 384-well PCR plates as sources and one 384-well plate as destination. First, dispense 12\u00b5L of water from reservoir to all wells in rows A and B of the pooling plate using P20 multichannel pipette. Then transfer 3\u00b5L samples from specific wells in each PCR plate following a predetermined pooling scheme where 4 samples from each source plate are consolidated into single destination wells, with plates 1 and 3 mapping to even-numbered columns and plates 2 and 4 to odd-numbered columns across rows A and B respectively.",
